      "description": "This 2004 Honda S2000 (AP2) is a superlative example of analog engineering, featuring the high-revving F22C1 inline-four engine and its signature VTEC engagement. The 6-speed close-ratio manual transmission offers short, crisp throws, channeling power to the rear wheels via a Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its legendary rigidity thanks to the X-bone frame construction, while the four-wheel double-wishbone suspension provides precise geometry under heavy lateral loads. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and a refresh of the gearbox and differential fluids using high-shear synthetic lubricants. Mechanically robust and ready for spirited driving, this S2000 delivers an unfiltered connection to the road.",
